  "hash_before": "7969bf54ba24174eed140d2199bf95c2694a423c62f9035378576c5eaaa98a47",
  "heading_path": "气体动理论 / 气体分子数按速率分布的统计规律",
  "intensity": "STRUCTURAL",
  "line_count": 80,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02770:3bb8b0881e9e]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02771:a515a390a32d]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02772:9e0818fc5dc4]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02773:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n（1）[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02774:12819bbfb8b5]]\n（2）速率在 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02775:6ddb34f094aa]] 内的 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02776:a5c96462c49a]] 个分子总动能：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02777:836be35d8727]]所以速率在 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02778:796477244d42]] 内所有分子的动能和：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02779:59072ccc1f20]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02780:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02781:e004873c394e]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02782:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02783:2ad9e70450bf]]\n由于 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02784:5766ec8054c9]] 到 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02785:aac924539a24]] 区间内各速率出现得同样频繁，平均速率落在中点 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02786:d1680bfd3c06]] 很自然；若把 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02787:3878a63b80f4]] 误当成分子数密度而不做归一化，就会失去这个统计意义。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02788:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02789:dec8dd7428c1]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02790:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n最概然速率的基本式是\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02791:302e6e76d7dd]] \n但题目没有直接给温度和摩尔质量。此时要把状态方程 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02792:54449ab70bb4]] 与总质量 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02793:925ed0456051]] 合起来，把 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02794:2fae270451d9]] 换成宏观量。\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02795:99c196b1c646]] \n代入数据，\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02796:6ae3c24341dc]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02797:d0c4b394b8a8]] 的量纲是 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02798:3acce97225e3]]，开方后正好是速率；这里的 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02799:12e37fa4f9bb]] 是气体总质量，而不是摩尔质量。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02800:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02801:48f0c0d3cb13]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02802:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n先认出右侧峰值对应的是轻分子氢气，因为同温下轻分子跑得更快。接着不用重推分布函数，只需抓住\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02803:754129d74e2b]] \n给出的质量依赖关系。\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02804:9ba10190ebd2]] \n于是右侧读数就是 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02805:130689dd7d1e]]，氧气的最概然速率为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02806:98e53b694494]]。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02807:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n",
  "mode": "REWRITE",
